survey_response.review_text: Dr. Suneetha is one of the finest dentists in the city. She has been our family dentist since many years. She is known for the right diagnosis, hassle-free treatment, friendliness and modesty. I highly recommend Dr. Suneetha for any sort of dental issues!
I would highly recommend cosme dental for anyone who has dental problems, the doctors here are very skilled.

Dr Suneeta madam is very good asset to the hospital. The way she treats and explains the issue is awesome. She used to educate the patients and attendants regarding the issues and later her suggestions are excellent. Mr SreeRam Kumar too extends his friendliness and ease of interacting and suggestions on issues are highly thankful. The clinic is good for Nizampet and surrounding people. Thanks to one and all of the staff of the clinic.- Sreeram, h/o Vijayalakshmi

Very polite, friendly approach, explains the problem and gives the solution. Excellent treatment . Good atmosphere of clinic. Very good attendance. Prompt in maintaining the time and date of appointment. Very good follow up and enquiries about the patient after the treatment. We can get the apartments at our convenience and they oblige. All the doctors are technically excellent. Their approach in attempting the problem is commendable. The location of the Hospital is very convenient to all.

I had a tooth ache and its because my wisdom tooth was aligned differently then my other tooth and was pushing the tooth next to it. I had a sensation for two weeks, that eventually turned into ache. I visited the doctor a couple of days ago and she took an xray that showed the problem. The doctor suggested that I get my wisdom tooth removed surgically, and I got it done the next day (yesterday). The procedure lasted about 45 min, and I did experience some pain during the course. However, the overall procedure was smooth and my pain reduced significantly after 24 hrs. I asked the doctor to give me as little medication as possible, and the doctor obliged, and gave me all the precautions I need to take. I have a follow up review today, and hope everything will go well.

The doctor is very down to earth, listens patiently and is very approachable unlike my previous dentist. She gives you a belief that she'll take good care and solve your problem. I'm really happy with the way the doctor treated me, and I would recommend the doctor and the clinic to my family and friends.
